preference.name: AWS_allowedTypesForDelete
preference.preference_description: Defines the list of Business Object types for which the "Delete" command is visible. Making the "Delete" command visible does not enable deleting the Business Object type. Currently only limited types support an intelligent delete that breaks relations and then deletes the object, e.g. folders and datasets.
